        <strong>${dominantName}</strong> is the primary deity candidate: ${dominant?.isInterior?'an interior planet, confined to dawn and dusk — generating a theology of liminal beauty, impermanence, and the threshold between worlds':'an exterior planet, roaming the full night sky — generating a theology of authority, abundance, and the long cycle'}. Its mean brightness when visible is <em>${dominant?.meanBVis.toExponential(3)}</em>, and it is midnight-capable <em>${((dominant?.midFrac||0)*100).toFixed(1)}%</em> of the time.<br><br>
